  <!-- ══════════════════════════════════════ SECTION 13: FINAL ASSIGNMENT ══ -->
  <section id="s13-final-proj" class="docs-section">
    <h2 class="docs-section-title">§13 — Final Assignment</h2>
    <p>The capstone project — a substantial deliverable unlocked after passing the final test. Supports milestones for phased submission.</p>
    <div class="docs-pre">
      <div class="docs-pre__bar"><span class="docs-pre__dot"></span><span class="docs-pre__dot"></span><span class="docs-pre__dot"></span><span class="docs-pre__lang">yaml</span></div>
