  <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════ SECTION 17: DISCUSSION ══ -->
  <section id="s17-discussion" class="docs-section">
    <h2 class="docs-section-title">§17 — Discussion</h2>
    <p>Enable GitHub Discussions integration. When <code>per_chapter: true</code>, the bot creates a pinned discussion thread when each chapter unlocks.</p>
    <div class="docs-pre">
      <div class="docs-pre__bar"><span class="docs-pre__dot"></span><span class="docs-pre__dot"></span><span class="docs-pre__dot"></span><span class="docs-pre__lang">yaml</span></div>
      <code>discussion:
  enabled: true
  category: "Course Q&amp;A"
  per_chapter: true
  pinned_resources:
